About Bain Capital Private Equity






Bain Capital Private Equity pioneered the value added investment approach. We partner with our management teams to provide the strategic and analytic resources needed to build and grow great companies. Our success is built on a collaborative approach that harnesses the power of great teams to generate the best ideas and strategies. Since 1984, we’ve made over 270 investments that have generated industry leading returns while building a global network of highly trained team members that are committed to the success of our portfolio companies. We are proud that Bain Capital professionals in aggregate are the largest investor in every fund we raise. This commitment highlights our core principle of alignment with our investors and management teams. 










 



 Strategy 

Our consulting heritage is at the very core of our strategy.  We partner with management teams to improve their operations and to build great companies. 

read more » 





 



 History 

Since 1984, we have raised 18 private equity funds including global, European and Asian-focused funds. 

read more » 





 



 Community 

Our people are committed to making a difference in the communities in which we live and work, devoting time and energy to a wide range of charitable and community organizations. 

read more » 





 



 Regions 

We operate as one firm – our private equity effort reflects one globally integrated team operating across eight offices on three continents. 

read more » 





 



 Portfolio Support 

Working in partnership with exceptional management teams, Bain Capital Private Equity's people, capital and vision have helped to build and strengthen the companies in which we invest. 

read more » 





 



 Investors 

We build long-term relationships with our Limited Partners founded on the principle of alignment of interests. We are proud that the majority of our Limited Partners have invested with us for well over a decade. 

read more » 





 














































History | Bain Capital Private Equity














Skip to main content 




Bain Capital Private Equity









