Bain Capital Asia Fund III LP: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 3:53 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Bain Capital Asia Fund III LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Bain Capital Asia Fund III LP specializes in buyout investments. The fund seeks to invest in a range of sectors including service, consumer-focused businesses, consumer products and financial services. It prefers to invest in Asia and Asia-Pacific regions with a focus on China, Japan, India, and Australia with the flexibility to invest in Southeast Asia and South Korea.


John Hancock Tower200 Clarendon StreetBoston, MA 02116United StatesFounded in 2015



Phone: 617-516-2000

Fax: 617-516-2010








